00:00:55.690 --> 00:01:01.739
Pour this into your apples, give it a good
stir around, and just leave this for another

00:01:01.739 --> 00:01:08.050
couple of minutes; just to thicken up that
sauce.

00:01:08.050 --> 00:01:14.070
The corn flour makes this sauce in the apples;
makes all those juices lovely and thick, and

00:01:14.070 --> 00:01:15.550
syrupy.

00:01:15.550 --> 00:01:17.030
Okay.

00:01:17.030 --> 00:01:20.760
