00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:43.080
Yeah.

00:01:43.080 --> 00:01:46.160
Now leave this to one side, and you can make
your crumble topping now.

00:01:46.160 --> 00:01:52.000
Just add your flour.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.550
Next your cold butter cut into cubes.

00:01:54.550 --> 00:01:55.550
Sugar.

00:01:55.550 --> 00:02:02.540
